name: Black Cat
description:
A Reggae approach from The Last Armed Forces. Recorded from the home studio in Crystal Palace, London. Experimental in the sense that truly epitomizes The Last Armed Forces, you can hear everything from Roots Reggae, Dub, Drum and Bass and even some Dubstep that creeps in on the last track.

A unique listen for all Reggae fans.
